Asma Fahmi was walking to her car with her family when they were attacked by three men from a balcony . 
  The 34-year-old was with her sister and ill mother when they had hard boiled eggs pelted at their heads . 
  Asma came to Australia from Syria when she was four years old . 
  She has been attacked twice in Sydney in four years . 
  She said that many victims of racial abuse have no faith in the legal system . 
  She took her ill mother to a screening of Les Miserables . 
 